attributes.description: This dashboard provides an overview of the findings collected by the AWS Security Hub integration.

embeddableConfig.content:
This dashboard provides an overview of findings collected by the AWS Security Hub integration.

The dashboard highlights finding trends over time and displays the total number of findings, followed by the metrics for open and closed findings. It also features table charts showing the top resources with the highest number of findings, a pie chart that breaks down findings by severity, and a bar chart that shows the breakdown of findings by status and product name.

[**Integration Page**](/app/integrations/detail/aws_securityhub/overview)
